env PAGER=cat man timing_library_infer_cap_range_from_ccs_receiver _model
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_library...receiver_model(25.10)  timing_library...receiver_model(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_infer_cap_range_from_ccs_receiver_model

Syntax
        timing_library_infer_cap_range_from_ccs_receiver_model

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Infers  the  rise or fall of capacitance range values from CCS receiver
       capacitance model.

       When set to false, the rise/fall CCS capacitance range values  are  not
       inferred.  The NLDM pin capacitance range values defined in the library
       are honored.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

